      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beacon_Theatre_(New_York_City)"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Singer and Kerr transformed the Beacon into a rock club in 1974, and by 1976 it became a performing‑arts center.",
