      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beacon_Theatre_(New_York_City)"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "In 2006, the Beacon staged the Zappa Plays Zappa concert, a tribute to musician Frank Zappa.",
